---
// web-public/src/pages/about.astro
import '../styles/global.css';

const pageTitle = "About - Tracking Project";
---

<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/Logo8.png" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-200 antialiased">
    <div class="fixed inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-slate-900 via-slate-950 to-slate-950 -z-10"></div>

    <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-white/5 bg-slate-950/80 backdrop-blur-md">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 group">
            <img 
                src="/Logo8.png" 
                alt="Logo" 
                class="h-8 w-8 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(168,85,247,0.8)]"
            />
            <span class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-100">Tracking<span class="text-purple-500">Project</span></span>
        </a>
        <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">&larr; Balik ke Home</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <section>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">
             Bukan Startup, Cuma <span class="text-purple-500">Resolusi.</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Jujur aja, gue capek cuma wacana "pengen bikin ini, pengen bikin itu" tapi gak pernah jadi.
            Tahun 2026 ini, gue bikin komitmen bodoh: <strong class="text-white">12 Project dalam 12 Bulan.</strong>
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="p-6 bg-slate-900/50 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-purple-500/30 transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Kenapa Tracking Project?</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">
            Website ini cuma dashboard buat gue (dan lu) ngeliat apakah gue konsisten atau akhirnya tumbang di tengah jalan.
            Semua project yang gue build bakal gue taruh di sini, lengkap sama statusnya: kelar, mangkrak, atau lagi kebakar deadline.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-400">
            Source code? Kemungkinan besar Open Source. Cek aja GitHub gue nanti.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Tools of Chaos</h3>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <li class="bg-slate-900 border border-white/10 p-3 rounded-lg text-center text-slate-300 text-sm">Astro / React</li>
            <li class="bg-slate-900 border border-white/10 p-3 rounded-lg text-center text-slate-300 text-sm">Bun (Speed!)</li>
            <li class="bg-slate-900 border border-white/10 p-3 rounded-lg text-center text-slate-300 text-sm">ElysiaJS</li>
            <li class="bg-slate-900 border border-white/10 p-3 rounded-lg text-center text-slate-300 text-sm">PostgreSQL</li>
            <li class="bg-slate-900 border border-white/10 p-3 rounded-lg text-center text-slate-300 text-sm">Drizzle ORM</li>
            <li class="bg-slate-900 border border-white/10 p-3 rounded-lg text-center text-slate-300 text-sm">Kopi Hitam</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <div class="pt-8 border-t border-white/10 text-center">
            <p class="text-slate-500 italic">"Done is better than perfect." - (Semoga gue inget quote ini)</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>